    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrc="shortdesc:1;5:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/dbdocsconcept1.dita">The NextGen Trading Card Game features exclusive collectible cards inspired by the
        Rocket Software NextGen Academy and its Rocketeers. The platform empowers users to buy and
        sell new cards and related products, creating a dynamic marketplace for fans and
        collectors.</shortdesc>
